_sText:
Top of a large building, An extreme close range office battle with small rooms and hiding places everywhere.
2 bombsites, You can jump off the edge and die if you want :P
Tons of props, May lag when bomb explodes.

Everything is in the .bsp, Custom textures, Nav, Overview map etc.

This is the Wednesday, 24 January 2007 version, And it is unlikely that there'll be versions after this.
